16c5b0e269a44045","tid":983882,"uid":176991,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T12:47:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> facebook睇到呢篇文講James Watson 偷人研究成果<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=1849134971874997\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fphoto.php%3Ffbid%3D1849134971874997&d=us0DE1UdPinnP7OaCz4lkE%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=f5875ee1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=1849134971874997</a><br />\n來自King's College的女科學家Rosalind Franklin和她當時的博士生最先拍到雙螺旋DNA照片，與她同校的科學家Wilkins則把照片拿給了從劍橋過來訪問的Watson看。Wilkins當時與Franklin極度不和。<br />\n<br />\nWatson看到DNA照片時震驚得血脈噴張，他與Crick原先研究出來的錯誤的DNA模型，在這一瞥之下立即煙消雲散。此時，Franklin已經準備離開實驗室，她在那裡遇到非常不友好的工作氣氛。<br />\n<br />\nWatson和Crick此後需要更具體的數據。Franklin研究所得的數據寫在了一份非正式的報告裏，在她不知情的情況下，由劍橋的Max Perutz經過一次轉手，落到了Watson和Crick的手上。文章說，報告並非confidential，但無疑劍橋獲得數據的方式是「不誠實的」。他們當然也沒有告訴King's College的人他們在做什麼，更沒有向Franklin詢問是否可以使用她的數據。<br />\n<br />\n諷刺的是，其實在此之前，Franklin已經在一個研討會上present過她的數據，而當時Watson也是觀眾之一。如果Watson有記筆記，而非顧著嘲笑Franklin的著裝品味和樣貌，他完全可以提早在他們獲得突破性發現的15個月前，就能把如此關鍵的數據提供給Crick。<br />\n<br />\n文章提到，Franklin當時在實驗室所面對的環境，是被孤立以及無法找到任何人與她交流意見。在這樣惡劣的條件下，她所作出的進展無疑是卓越的。她的筆記本顯示，她已經看到了DNA最關鍵的秘密：它的序列蘊含著遺傳密碼。<br />\n<br />\n可是她已經沒有機會去證明她的發現，因為Watson和Crick此時已經衝線&mdash;&mdash;站在她的照片和數據基礎之上。"},{"pid":"a0c1d85332b8ffed0c650229a72866a89bfb6736","tid":983882,"uid":224928,"like":8,"dislike":4,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T12:48:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"feb5c8db5215e3f6c0fbe80198c6f0d5652f636a","tid":983882,"uid":176991,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"8e85d471abeaa10026d726887f3373dd3aea179f","tid":983882,"uid":26601,"like":94,"dislike":11,"score":83,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T11:57:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pics.me.me/greece-2500-years-ago-rome-2000-years-ago-china-1800-7087767.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpics.me.me%2Fgreece-2500-years-ago-rome-2000-years-ago-china-1800-7087767.png&h=392f9287&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n肯定唔關基因事<br />\n一定係教育問題<br />\n其他國家都有外星人教，唯獨非洲黑人冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T12:49:41.000Z","msg":"拎間up dup矛屋同啲出名建築比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  非洲一樣有出名嘅wonders"},{"pid":"475de169214f0837b4be547318b614ae9be9334f","tid":983882,"uid":49136,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"quote":{"pid":"a0c1d85332b8ffed0c650229a72866a89bfb6736","tid":983882,"uid":224928,"like":8,"dislike":4,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"8b4b4412abc25ed73e8acefba6e7d36c86326b57","tid":983882,"uid":49136,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T11:51:43.000Z","msg":"所以黑人唔蠢、體能又強、撚又長？<br />\n黑人至上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T12:48:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T12:52:00.000Z","msg":"華人唔聰明、體能又差、又冇肌肉、又短撚，仲要細眼<br />\n唔怪得港女愛洋腸"},{"pid":"a885054f12666dd549e151cd38cd17e66d8e8c2a","tid":983882,"uid":224928,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T12:52:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1236f75bcce314741c95e6c807652715875d79d2","tid":983882,"uid":49136,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"a885054f12666dd549e151cd38cd17e66d8e8c2a","tid":983882,"uid":224928,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"475de169214f0837b4be547318b614ae9be9334f","tid":983882,"uid":49136,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"quote":{"pid":"a0c1d85332b8ffed0c650229a72866a89bfb6736","tid":983882,"uid":224928,"like":8,"dislike":4,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T12:48:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T12:52:00.000Z","msg":"華人唔聰明、體能又差、又冇肌肉、又短撚，仲要細眼<br />\n唔怪得港女愛洋腸"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T12:52:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T12:53:49.000Z","msg":"屌 科大多gay佬一定有科大根據<img src=\"/assets/f